These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, british, australian, chinese
1. the british is in an odd position##4
2. the chinese is between the mexican and the british##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | mexican | chinese | british | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, cranberry, corn, lettuce
1. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | cranberry | blueberry | lettuce | corn |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, fantasy, epic, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | epic | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, swimming, basketball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | swimming | biathlon | cricket | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
