2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | baseball | climbing | golf | tennis |

