.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, ship, motorbike
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | ship | taxi | motorbike | skateboard |

